      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=691</guid>
      <description>Did you know that you can become an affiliate marketer for peanuts and make a great income by building many niche targeted sites?
You sure can.  The internet is full of affiliate products and if you create a site, get it set up, get links to it and target your main keyword phrase you can be [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Internet_Marketing_Affiliate_Program_Still_Successful.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/affiliates.jpg"><a href="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/affiliates.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-694" title="affiliates" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/affiliates-300x261.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="261" /></a></a></p>
<p>Did you know that you can become an affiliate marketer for peanuts and make a great income by building many niche targeted sites?</p>
<p>You sure can.  The internet is full of affiliate products and if you create a site, get it set up, get links to it and target your main keyword phrase you can be making money in no time.</p>
<p>Now lets say that one site you have makes you $5.00 per day from Adsense. That might not seem like much but if you have 15 or 20 niche sites you just built yourself an internet business income system that can run on autopilot!</p>
<p>So keep this ind when you are planning your next home based business idea.</p>
