    <item>
      <title>Ways to Profit from a Niche Business Idea – #1 in this Series</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/ways-profit-niche-business-idea-1-series/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/ways-profit-niche-business-idea-1-series/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Sep 2009 17:57:08 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Making Money On The Internet]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=635</guid>
      <description>#1 Way to Profit from your Niche Business Idea:
Take your Micro Niche and hire a freelance writer on http://www.elance.com or wherever you can find ghostwriters and create an ebook surrounding a particularly hot topic that surrounds your niche. Of if you would like to take on the task yourself. . . http://www.7dayebook.com
Go check out different [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Ways_to_Profit_from_a_Niche_Business_Idea__1_in_this_Series.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-636" style="margin: 6px;" title="Making money on the internet with ebooks" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/ebooklogo.jpg" alt="Making money on the internet with ebooks" width="120" height="87" />#1 Way to Profit from your Niche Business Idea:</strong><br />
Take your <em>Micro Niche</em> and hire a freelance writer on http://www.elance.com or wherever you can find ghostwriters and create an ebook surrounding a particularly hot topic that surrounds your niche. Of if you would like to take on the task yourself. . . http://www.7dayebook.com</p>
<p>Go check out different forums and blogs that may be discussing the topic you wish to expose. You can do this by searching Wordpress blogs, Google blogs, Technorati, Ezinearticles.com, ArticleCity, Go Articles, Wikipedia etc.</p>
<p>Hang around and figure out what people are anxious and concerned about. This is KEY.  Or, you can take this and take it to the next level, and create products for a specific target market, and sell resell rights to the products to take home more money at the end of the day. You can even sell your ebook rights on eBay for a fixed amount.</p>
<p>Better yet, to balloon the idea, create multiple products you sell the rights to and bundle it all together in one sale.</p>
<p>There are many products out there that talk about how to create Private Label Rights products, should you desire to dig further.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/ways-profit-niche-business-idea-1-series/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
      <enclosure url="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Ways_to_Profit_from_a_Niche_Business_Idea__1_in_this_Series.mp3" length="727139" type="audio/mpeg" />
    </item>
