      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=628</guid>
      <description>#2 Way to Profit from your Niche Business Idea:
No one says you have to stick to affiliate marketing to create an online gold mine without having a physical product.  Here&amp;#8217;s what you can do:
Create a private membership site and (charge either a monthly fee or a yearly fee) around a particular topic that delivers a [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Ways_to_Profit_from_a_Niche_Business_Idea__2_in_this_Series.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-633" style="margin: 6px;" title="Making money on the internet" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/membersonly.jpg" alt="Making money on the internet" width="92" height="124" />#2 Way to Profit from your Niche Business Idea:</strong></p>
<p>No one says you have to stick to affiliate marketing to create an online gold mine without having a physical product.  Here&#8217;s what you can do:</p>
<p>Create a private membership site and (charge either a monthly fee or a yearly fee) around a particular topic that delivers a solution (preferably a long term solution).</p>
<p>It&#8217;s very easy to set up a membership area that is all automated.  I use Sentrylogin.com which costs me $4.95 per month to have my site secure and they take care of processing my payments through Paypal.  That means that after you create your website, you then turn it into a membership site where people can register, get a password and login without you having to be at your computer 24/7.  You will want this all automated so you can focu on creating content for your members.</p>
<p>A great example of this is my http://www.businessideascenter.com membership site. In fact, the site delivers a specific solution to starting an online home based business and how that’s done.  The site does very well in a high competition market because it is unique and helps people solve a problem.  The site is filled with step-by-step videos, enormous value above and beyond the $99 membership fee.</p>
<p>And that goes without saying that you must deliver on your promise, and in most cases, OVER-DELIVER to people. And they will stay your loyal customer… for life!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/ways-profit-niche-business-idea-2-series/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
      <enclosure url="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Ways_to_Profit_from_a_Niche_Business_Idea__2_in_this_Series.mp3" length="865121" type="audio/mpeg" />
