      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Making Money On The Internet]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=625</guid>
      <description>#3 Way to Profit from your Niche Business Idea:
In this series of making money on the internet here is a fantastic way to offer a service, if you will, because you are supplying all the information someone is looking for and are using ads to generate your income.
Create an article site and monetize it with [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Ways_to_Profit_from_a_Niche_Business_Idea__3_in_this_Series.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-626" style="margin: 6px;" title="googleone" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/googleone.jpg" alt="googleone" width="150" height="60" /><strong>#3 Way to Profit from your Niche Business Idea:</strong></p>
<p>In this series of making money on the internet here is a fantastic way to offer a service, if you will, because you are supplying all the information someone is looking for and are using ads to generate your income.<br />
Create an article site and monetize it with Pay-Per-Click traffic and Google Adsense preferably.</p>
<p>You could collect articles from a group of individuals within your topic of interest or start a larger more broad article directory that covers many topics, like http://www.ezinearticles.com If you click onto an article specific page at the link above, you’ll see Google Adsense on the page, and I believe the site owner of EzineArticles.com makes more in a<br />
day from Adsense than most people make in a month. Let’s just say to most people that figure is not even in the realm of possibility.</p>
<p>Once you establish a hot article directory, you’ll get some true love from Google as well as fuel more submissions from your all your authors and publishers.  Then, once you build visitors to the independent articles that get submitted, it’s<br />
just a matter of science in the percentage of people that click on a paid ad that generates a commission to simply increasing your traffic to increase your pay.</p>
<p>Don’t look at it as simple work – nothing really is.  Making money on the internet does take dedication, work and the right know-how.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/ways-profit-niche-business-idea-3-series/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
