      <title>The 3 UNBREAKABLE Golden Rules of SEO</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/1-home-based-business/3-unbreakable-golden-rules-seo/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/1-home-based-business/3-unbreakable-golden-rules-seo/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Aug 2009 14:15:28 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[1 Home Based Business]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=498</guid>
      <description>My friends at Market Samurai have this to say about the 3 Unbreakable golden rules of seo!

Golden Rule #1:
The Fact: 90% Of All Keywords Have NO Traffic – Therefore, You Must ONLY Target Keywords with Significant Traffic To Warrant Investing Any Time or Effort In.
The Risk: Break This Rule And You’ll Never Attract Any Significant [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-The_3_UNBREAKABLE_Golden_Rules_of_SEO.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="font-size: small;"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-509" style="margin: 6px;" title="3 Unbreakable rules to seo" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/08/market-samurai-image.gif" alt="3 Unbreakable rules to seo" width="106" height="129" />My friends at Market Samurai have this to say about the 3 Unbreakable golden rules of seo!<br />
</span></span><br />
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Golden Rule #1:</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The Fact: </span></strong>90% Of All Keywords Have NO Traffic – Therefore, You Must ONLY Target Keywords with Significant Traffic To Warrant Investing Any Time or Effort In.<br />
<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The Risk: </span></strong>Break This Rule And You’ll Never Attract Any Significant Traffic… And You Will FAIL.</span></span><br />
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Golden Rule #2:</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The Fact: </span></strong>Many Keywords With Traffic Have Little Commercial Value (“Tire Kicker” Keywords) – Therefore, You Must ONLY Target Keywords With Significant PROFIT POTENTIAL.<br />
<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The Risk: </span></strong>Break This Rule And You’ll Only Attract “Browsers” NOT “Buyers”, And You’ll Unknowingly Select The Low Profit “Dog” Keywords, when for the SAME EFFORT You&#8217;ll Be Picking Keywords With 5, 10 Even 100 Times the Profit Potential! Clearly, If You Ignore This Golden Rule… You Will FAIL!</span></span><br />
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Golden Rule #3: </span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The Fact:</span></strong> Unfortunately, for Most Marketers, 90% Of Most Keywords Are Simply TOO COMPETITIVE To Rank Page #1 For…  &#8211; You Must ONLY Target Keywords That Have “Acceptable Competition” – That You Can REALISTICALLY RANK FOR!<br />
<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The Risk:</span></strong> You Need To Have A Systematic, Analytical Way To Analyze Your Competition (Like the “4-Phase” Competition Approach That Market Samurai Provides), Otherwise You’ll Have No Chance of Ranking At All&#8230; And You Will FAIL</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana,geneva;"><span style="font-size: small;">As always, we use Market Samurai to find these little gem keywords quickly and easily.  To learn how to build and promote a #1 home based business around your keyword (or any other niche you’re interested in) visit <a title="Business Ideas Center" rel="external" href="http://www.businessideascenter.com">The Business Ideas Center</a>.</span></span></p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/1-home-based-business/3-unbreakable-golden-rules-seo/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
      <enclosure url="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-The_3_UNBREAKABLE_Golden_Rules_of_SEO.mp3" length="877341" type="audio/mpeg" />
    </item>
