    <item>
      <title>Okay Moms, It’s Time To Start Your Own Home Based Business!</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/home-based-small-business/ladies-time-start-home-based-business/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/home-based-small-business/ladies-time-start-home-based-business/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Aug 2009 14:21:15 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Home Based Small Business]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Making Money On The Internet]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=455</guid>
      <description>I know there are a lot of moms out there searching the web looking for a home based business idea so that they can stay home and raise their kids and still earn an income.  I did the same thing for years while I stayed home with my younger daughter.  I needed to [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Okay_Moms_Its_Time_To_Start_Your_Own_Home_Based_Business.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I know there are a lot of moms out there searching the web looking for a home based business idea so that they can stay home and raise their kids and still earn an income.  I did the same thing for years while I stayed home with my younger daughter.  I needed to make enough money to help pay my bills but I also wanted to stay home.</p>
<p>It didn&#8217;t make sense for me to go back to a job that only made it possible to pay the daycare expenses of a newborn.  And in my town of Marlborough the cost for daycare for a newborn was 350.00 per week.</p>
<p>I couldn&#8217;t see doing that.  I just wanted to be home with my baby.  (And of course make some money so my husband didn&#8217;t kill me!)</p>
<p>So now that I run a successful company I want to invite moms who want to stay home and find a profitable, safe, legitimate way to <a href="http://www.businessideascenter.com">make money online</a> to see what they can do with the Business Ideas Center.  See how affiliate marketing can be profitable while you are in total control over it.  You can easily create your new business and promote online products from companies like Amazon.com and Google and Clickbank.  No scams.  No lies.  Just real ideas, products and keywords, training videos, real companies and real businesses.  This is for women all over the world that want to be taken seriously.</p>
<p>And I am always available to help them.  I am not lounging on my 75 foot yacht in the Caribbean or sitting on my island oasis.  I am sitting in my home office writing this and in just a few weeks I&#8217;ll be putting my 2nd grader on the bus for school.</p>
<p>Now that&#8217;s what I call paradise!<a title="School Bus" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/21484712@N00/3708011885/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0pt none;" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2612/3708011885_c6e75e820b_m.jpg" border="0" alt="School Bus" width="240" height="160" /></a></p>
<p><small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="../wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Caitlinator" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/21484712@N00/3708011885/" target="_blank">Caitlinator</a></small></p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/home-based-small-business/ladies-time-start-home-based-business/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
