    <item>
      <title>How Do You Create Natural Backlinks?</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/create-natural-backlinks/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/create-natural-backlinks/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Aug 2009 14:40:44 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Making Money On The Internet]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[How Do You Create Natural Backlinks]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Small Business Idea]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=452</guid>
      <description>When you finish your new home based small business you are going to want to create backlinks to your site in order to rank better in the search engines.  So how do you go about doing that?  Google is looking to see how you are doing it too so please be careful when [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-How_Do_You_Create_Natural_Backlinks.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>When you finish your new home based small business you are going to want to create backlinks to your site in order to rank better in the search engines.  So how do you go about doing that?  Google is looking to see how you are doing it too so please be careful when thinking about this.</p>
<p>There are linking farms out there that you can pay to get backlinks but they are typically black hat so it&#8217;s best to stay away from them.  You want to create natural or organic backlinks and to do so may take some time on your part but trust me, you won&#8217;t get knocked out of ranking from Google.</p>
<p>Here are a few ways I create one way backlinks to my own sites.  I find related sites that I can leave comments on with my web site address and I actually read the comments and put my opinion in.  Don&#8217;t be spammy here.  Seriously take a few minutes and read what people are talking about and become an expert in your field and offer your opinion.</p>
<p>Another way I get back links is by creating additional pages in Squidoo and Hubpages and adding your links to your websites from there.  It&#8217;s easy and keeping it up to date only takes a few minutes a day.  You&#8217;ll like the links.</p>
<p>Also I create a podcast for my site and submit it to the podcast directories.  You can also join blog carnivals and get great backlinks that way.  Start bookmarking your posts too!</p>
<p>So really do some work and get those natural backlinks you need.  It will be well worth your time in the long run.  You want to create a <a href="http://www.businessideascenter.com">money making internet business</a> without it being banished from Google.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/create-natural-backlinks/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
