    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Is There Anything Besides Taking Surveys That A Home Based Businesses Can Do?</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/surveys-home-based-businesses/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/surveys-home-based-businesses/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Aug 2009 14:39:31 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Making Money On The Internet]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[make money online surveys]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=443</guid>
      <description>Absolutely!
In fact, I would highly recommend it.  And that is to get yourself into affiliate marketing where you have complete control over what you will be promoting and for whom.
You see, the problem with taking surveys is that you are reliant upon the companies sending you a survey that is geared toward your age, race, [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Is_There_Anything_Besides_Taking_Surveys_That_A_Home_Based_Businesses_Can_Do.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-447" style="margin: 6px;" title="surveys" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/08/j0427676.jpg" alt="surveys" width="154" height="232" />Absolutely!</p>
<p>In fact, I would highly recommend it.  And that is to get yourself into affiliate marketing where you have complete control over what you will be promoting and for whom.</p>
<p>You see, the problem with taking surveys is that you are reliant upon the companies sending you a survey that is geared toward your age, race, sex, interests etc.  I am a 45 year old  married woman with kids and because of my age I rarely would get surveys.  If the companies are not sending you any surveys there is no money.  The money is small so you would need to take a lot of surveys to even make any amount of money and that is going to be a total time hog.</p>
<p>Instead of spending all your time taking surveys which in reality is limited by how many hours in a day you can spend online and how many surveys you are sent, why not build an empire of your own that will eventually run on it&#8217;s own so you can keep building it up?  Why not be in total control of your time and energy!</p>
<p>In a nutshell, in order to run your own affiliate business you will need an idea, a product(s), a domain name, a hosting company, a blog and the rest is getting your site out there with targeted keywords and by building organic links.  Sure this may sound confusing to someone just starting out but there are many resources to help you do this.  Okay, we are THE resource to help you do all of what I just said!</p>
<p>Affiliate marketing is a billion dollar business and it works.  And it&#8217;s easy to do.  Here at the Business Ideas Center that&#8217;s all we do is <a href="http://www.businessideascenter.com">affiliate marketing</a>.  We give our members ideas that are marketable, we show them what affiliate products they could promote through the top 4 affiliate marketing companies and the keywords they need to use to promote the products.  This puts our members in complete control over what they want to earn commissions from and how many companies they want to promote.  Basically the sky is the limit. We even show them with our video training library how to choose a domain name, hosting company and how to set up their blog.</p>
<p>Don&#8217;t be afraid to be more than you can imagine!  Taking surveys may be great for someone wanting a little extra cash at the end of the month for a decent chunk of their time but if you are truly looking to build a home based business than DO IT.</p>
<p>So here is my recommendation &#8211; forget the surveys and start your own business.  It&#8217;s cheap to start and unlimited in potential!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/surveys-home-based-businesses/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
