      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I used to get very confused about RSS too until I researched it.  Then I was only half as confused!</p>
<p>I didn&#8217;t fully understand what RSS was and what to do with it until I played around with my blog and started submitting it to the RSS sites.  So I want to see if perhaps I can help you understand what the heck RSS is!</p>
<p>I learn by seeing, you know&#8230;videos&#8230;live presentations&#8230;not by reading a manual.  And I pick it up quickly once I&#8217;ve seen it done so I made a video from my site to show you. &#8211; Hope this help!</p>
