      <description>Some of the best business opportunities are the one&amp;#8217;s that won&amp;#8217;t cost you thousands of dollars to start.
At the Business Ideas Center you can enroll for a year which allows you unlimited ideas with their keyword phrases already selected based on competition, traffic and marketability, plus you get all the training videos on how to [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/business-ideas-center/Business_Ideas_Center-Best_Business_Opportunities.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Some of the best business opportunities are the one&#8217;s that won&#8217;t cost you thousands of dollars to start.</p>
<p>At the Business Ideas Center you can enroll for a year which allows you unlimited ideas with their keyword phrases already selected based on competition, traffic and marketability, plus you get all the training videos on how to set up your site and start promoting it. There is a resource section with hundreds of links and tools to help you work better.  Now this is all for $99.00 a year.  If you think about it, you could easily start 10 new businesses promoting affiliate products (which is a billion dollar empire) which would then be at an average cost of only 10 bucks.  So what is it worth to you?</p>
<p>Now if you were to try to do all of the above without any assistance you wouldn&#8217;t even know where to start.  It took my years and a whole lot of money to learn every trick I know and how to quickly and effectively get a site up and running.</p>
<p>The best business opportunity is also one that you are comfortable getting into and that means you should know what is involved and what is included.  If the site shows you pictures of the owners on their yachts and in front of their new cars don&#8217;t believe it.  They are playing with your head and it will be a scam. Please be careful with what you sign up for.</p>
<p>Check out the Business Ideas Center and <a href="http://www.businessideascenter.com">start making money on the internet</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
