      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Are you trying to come up with an internet work at home job?  It isn&#8217;t easy sifting through the garbage and coming up with something that is honest huh?</p>
<p>I know.</p>
<p>In fact take a look at this email I received which I DID NOT click to open because it is a scam.  But unfortunately it is giving eBay a bad name.  You can make money on eBay but look at this guy&#8217;s promises.  He knows we are desperate to make money and he knows we have probably heard of eBay so he is giving us the impression of trust. </p>
<p>If you want to sell with eBay, go to eBay&#8217;s website and watch the free videos in the training sessions to learn the right way to sell on eBay so you don&#8217;t lose your money to a scam like this one below.<br />
__________________________</p>
<p><em>Ever heard of the eBay ca$h machine ?</p>
<p>&#8220;How would you like an extra $250 &#8211; $1000 a week on eBay with 15 minutes of your time ?&#8221;</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve made it my job to help people succeed online.<br />
I&#8217;m constantly on the lookout for the best ways and means to make your job simpler, and I pass the good stuff on to you.</p>
<p>I have developed the eBay Cash Machine &#8211; it allows everyone to make a great income on eBay 99% automatically. It only takes a few minutes to set up and once that is done you will have your own eBay Businesses that literally run on auto-pilot!<br />
You just wait for the money to come in!</p>
<p>I have found a foolproof method how anyone can easily make an extra $250, $500 or even $1000 per week on eBay using my eBay Ca$h Machine.?</p>
<p>Now before I get to deep into the details let me tell you what the eBay Ca$h Machine ISN&#8217;T.</p>
<p>It is NOT a promote my affiliate program to make m.oney!<br />
It is NOT a NOT A Get-Rich Q.uick Scheme!<br />
