      <category><![CDATA[website ideas]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=395</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[When I first started designing websites I used a web tool called Frontpage which was created by Microsoft.  It was a tool that I taught myself how to use over the course of a few months and my husband who is a huge computer nerd helped me on the really difficult parts to learn! [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>When I first started designing websites I used a web tool called Frontpage which was created by Microsoft.  It was a tool that I taught myself how to use over the course of a few months and my husband who is a huge computer nerd helped me on the really difficult parts to learn!  I built many sites with that tool and it was great for what I needed to do.  </p>
<p>But what if you don&#8217;t want to build sites from scratch or take the time to learn a tool like that?  </p>
<p>Nowadays you can create your domain and be up and running in a day with a professional and fantastic looking site.  It&#8217;s done with a blog.  You can use a theme that suits your style by picking from thousands available and all you need to do is start adding your posts which act as your content.  Its fresh and the search engines LOVE it.</p>
<p>Add some great photos to it and some affiliate products and you&#8217;re in business!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
