      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Here&#8217;s a top home based business idea that has a nice appeal to it because of the market trend that it follows.  And that is anything &#8220;back-to-school&#8221; orientated.  This being August 1st, our kids are going to be going back to school in just 4 weeks so if you have a cool product or have an affiliate product that you can start marketing RIGHT NOW, then do it!</p>
<p>Find the right keywords and start blogging quickly, bookmarking, and making some quick relationships so you can jump on this bandwagon.  For this particular trend I might suggest doing some targeted Google Ad Words because you might not have enough time to make it otherwise.  Compare advertising costs on Ad words to what you could be making and see if there is enough profit to go that route.  Ad Words gets your message out to millions in hours, not weeks.</p>
