      <description><![CDATA[
In my post yesterday I was saying that it is possible to earn extra money online but that it is going to take some time.  But what I wanted to tell you is how you can get money quickly if you need cash right away while you are building your ideas site.  There is a [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a title="Making money on the internet" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/9993075@N06/3731410460/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0pt none; margin: 6px;" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2450/3731410460_a156e1db1e_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Machines Finally Pay Out" width="240" height="160" /></a><br />
In my post yesterday I was saying that it is possible to earn extra money online but that it is going to take some time.  But what I wanted to tell you is how you can get money quickly if you need cash right away while you are building your ideas site.  There is a way without falling into a scam and my guess if just about everyone on the planet has heard of it.  And it&#8217;s not feeding money into a slot machine hoping you hit the jackpot!</p>
<p>Ebay.</p>
<p>Yup, Ebay.  You don&#8217;t need a web site or blog for this, you just need something to sell that people want to buy!</p>
<p>I know it might seem a little intimidating at first when you go on and look at auctions but I&#8217;ve done plenty of buying and selling on Ebay and it&#8217;s pretty easy.  I think the most important thing is to be very careful with your auction description, refund/exchanges policy, shipping procedure and price etc.  There are tons of manuals you can get from the library on how to sell on Ebay if you want to learn about it first.  Plus of course there is the whole help section from Ebay.  Read up on this BEFORE you start an auction.</p>
<p>Ebay allows you to sell quickly.  They keep a portion of your proceeds and so does PayPal if you are using them to do the money processing.  I highly recommend you use PayPal for that.  They are terrific.</p>
<p>So there you have it if you need a way to earn extra money while you are waiting for your main ideas to kick in.</p>
<p><small><a title="Attribution-ShareAlike License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="../wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="aresauburn™" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/9993075@N06/3731410460/" target="_blank">aresauburn™</a></small></p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/ways-earn-extra-money/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
