    <item>
      <title>Where to Build Your Computer Home Based Business</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/computer-work-at-home/computer-home-based-business-model/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/computer-work-at-home/computer-home-based-business-model/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2009 14:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Computer Work At Home]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[computer home based business]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=68</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[If you&#8217;re new to internet marketing or website building I want to strongly urge you to go the route of a blog as the platform for your new business.
Blogs are the number one fastest way to get your message across to the masses and here are just a few reasons why:

Search engines LOVE blogs!  Google [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-81" style="margin: 6px;" title="Wordpress for Computer Home Based Businesses" src="http://www.businessideascenter.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/wordpressforbusinessbloggers.jpg" alt="Wordpress for Computer Home Based Businesses" width="162" height="200" />If you&#8217;re new to internet marketing or website building I want to strongly urge you to go the route of a blog as the platform for your new business.</p>
<p>Blogs are the number one fastest way to get your message across to the masses and here are just a few reasons why:</p>
<ul>
<li>Search engines LOVE blogs!  Google seems to index blogs quickly so that&#8217;s your first major benefit right there.</li>
<li>It&#8217;s very easy to post fresh new content on your blog without website building knowledge.</li>
<li>Getting links are fairly easy because you can bookmark your content across social websites like Digg.com, delicious.com etc.</li>
<li>You&#8217;ll save a ton of money by not having to hire a web designer (that can run you hundreds and sometimes thousands of dollars.)</li>
</ul>
<p>I prefer to use the blogs at Wordpress.org with my own hosting company.  This way you get to have your own domain name and email address and more control over your blog.  When you have your own domain name you look more professional and people will put more trust into your business.  Plus going this way allows you so many more choices and control over how you can design your blog.</p>
<p>For example, this site for the Business Ideas Center is built with a Wordpress.org blog that I was able to just add my own images to the header to make it unique to my business and I have it hosted so I can have my own domain name (that&#8217;s the www.businessideascenter.com) and I can have my own email accounts.  If I had built the site with Expression Web or Dreamweaver I would have had to do a whole lot more work and I wouldn&#8217;t be able to have the blog section where people can make comments and interact with my business.  The way the web works now everyone wants to interact and get to know you.  By having a blog website you give them that opportunity.</p>
<p>If you won&#8217;t want to have your site hosted then go to Wordpress.com and get a blog there.  Your domain name will be tagged with Wordpress.com and you can just use an email account from Google or Yahoo or one of the other free email services.</p>
<p>Do yourself a favor and if you are setting up your computer home based business check out what blogs can do for you.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/computer-work-at-home/computer-home-based-business-model/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Do You Have Ideas For Your Small Business?</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/ideas-for-business/ideas-small-business/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/ideas-for-business/ideas-small-business/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2009 14:10:34 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Ideas For Business]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[ideas for small business]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=62</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[Every time I read a magazine, go to the dentist, have my hair styled, or go grocery shopping I can&#8217;t help but think of ways products could be better.  Luckily, not everyone has that insane curse!  I have spent almost 10 years developing new business products and ideas so after a while you [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a title="The Microwave" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/26266886@N00/3527637609/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="border: 0pt none; margin: 6px;" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2054/3527637609_256dd1d864_m.jpg" border="0" alt="The Microwave" width="216" height="162" /></a>Every time I read a magazine, go to the dentist, have my hair styled, or go grocery shopping I can&#8217;t help but think of ways products could be better.  Luckily, not everyone has that insane curse!  I have spent almost 10 years developing new business products and ideas so after a while you get pretty good at it.  But that&#8217;s not what I do now and for good reason.</p>
<p>There are problems with coming up with a new product idea or one that could be improved upon.  First of all it takes a lot of time.  Secondly, it&#8217;s a risk not knowing if the new product will sell or not and third is that it is expensive to develop the product.</p>
<p>So just how do I come up with ideas for small business wannabes?  I don&#8217;t reinvent the wheel; that&#8217;s how!  I find already existing products waiting to be sold that are in niche markets that have keywords that people are searching for which the big guys haven&#8217;t found.  Yup, if you have the right technology, the know-how and the experience to find them they are everywhere.</p>
<p>So don&#8217;t kill yourself thinking you have to come up with the next big product to hit the market since the microwave oven for your business idea.  Think easier, quicker and already in your face.</p>
<p><small><a title="Attribution License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="../wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Alan_D" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/26266886@N00/3527637609/" target="_blank">Alan_D</a></small></p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/ideas-for-business/ideas-small-business/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Making Money on the Internet?</title>
      <link>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/making-money-internet/</link>
      <comments>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/making-money-internet/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2009 19:53:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Business Ideas Center</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Making Money On The Internet]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.businessideascenter.com/?p=41</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[There are so many scams that I have personally seen when it comes to making money on the internet.  Please know that there are thousands of sites out there promising to make you rich quickly by following their plan.  Oh my gosh if I had a nickle for every person who fell for [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There are so many scams that I have personally seen when it comes to making money on the internet.  Please know that there are <strong>thousands </strong>of sites out there promising to make you rich quickly by following their plan.  Oh my gosh if I had a nickle for every person who fell for that&#8230;</p>
<p>I think I know the number one reason why they get so many people to &#8220;drink their cool aid&#8221; and that is because people are tired of the rat race, or they have lost their job, and are desperate for quick income.</p>
<p>It is tempting when they promise you the stars and moon and show you pictures of THEIR boats and cars.  Can I just tell you that I can photo shop myself with boats and cars too.  It&#8217;s pretty easy.</p>
<p>Anyway, find yourself an honest, well known company to help you get on your feet.  Can you make money on the internet without getting scammed?  Absolutely.  But do yourself a favor and if it sounds too good to be true don&#8217;t do it.  Because it will be.</p>
<p>Look at how other people are actually MAKING money on the internet and follow those people and those patterns.  Pretty soon you can tell the good guys from the bad guys!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.businessideascenter.com/making-money-on-the-internet/making-money-internet/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
    </item>
