      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I know you might be thinking, &#8220;That&#8217;s why I &#8216;m Here!&#8221; because you DON&#8217;T have a small business idea!  I have just added 5 more online business ideas that you can make money on the internet with and they are in the members section.  </p>
<p>Not a member?  You need to be!</p>
<p>Members of the Business Ideas Center have full access to the database of business ideas that have already had market research done on them, already had Google traffic keywords picked out for them and already have suggested domain names to help rank high in the search engines.   Members can then choose what idea they want to have completely turned into a search engine optimized blog/website.  And all the work has been done for them.  </p>
<p>Now you might also be thinking that this is all some automated program that just picks random topics and generates keywords that you&#8217;ll never be able to rank highly for.  Nope!  It couldn&#8217;t be further from that.</p>
<p>The Business Ideas Center is staffed by a HUMAN!  WOW!  That human is me&#8230;Nadine.  I have done all the market research, all the keyword research and know what domain names are the best.  I plow through the ideas weekly to make sure that they are still marketable and not saturated.  I also make sure that you have all the ground work done for you so that you can be that much further ahead of the game.  So basically I am saving you about 2 months worth of work!</p>
<p>So rather than say, “You really should find an idea that is marketable,” and send you off to muddle through it, you’ve now got one platform from which to get marketable, keyword ready, business ideas on which to choose from.</p>
<p>Alright, enough about that.  Get into the members area and grab your ready-to-go online business idea before someone else does.  It&#8217;s about as easy as plug and play!</p>
